room_title: Escape room "The Egyptian Tomb" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: Spent my husband's 40th birthday with family in the Egyptian pyramid. While we didn't escape, it was an absolute blast and we will be back!

room_title: Escape room "The Egyptian Tomb" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: This was our first time going to an escape room and we had a blast! We had a couple join our group and they were great! We did the Egyptian Room! Thanks, Andrew and Eric!

room_title: Escape room "The Egyptian Tomb" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
review: Yesterday was my 2nd visit and it was even more exciting than the first (and the first time was great in the Billionaire's Den). This time we did The Egyptian Tomb and we all have an amazing time. Great location and friendly staff! Can't wait to do the lab and the revolutionary room!
